snippet.textDisplay:
Three years ago, my big brother's girlfriend got married to someone else because his financial condition wasn’t good at the time. Back then, I was deeply in one-sided love too. My brother had told me to listen to this song, but I didn’t.

Now, when my own love has left me and gone to someone else — when my one-sided story has come to an end — I listen to that same song every day... with a pack of cigarettes.

Nam lene ka irada bhi na tha
Chal pada zikar tera bewajh....I do miss us...
But...
Maybe in next timeline..!
